Lately, Russia started to prepare for war in Asia. Japan on the other side, also braced themselves for war. After a while, Japan realised that Russia took ages to answer Japan’s demand and hesitated for weeks on end, therefore only playing 
for time in order to finish preparing for war. Hence, Japan called back their ambassador from Petersburg, meaning Japan is not ready anymore to negotiate with Russia, meaning Japan will protect their rights with a blade. On Sunday then, 
the war began.
